     just in case there is a collision.
     Alternatively, list the resources at the method level (they're in the tree...) but that looks really messy. Make it expandable? 
                  <li>Resources
                      <ul class="nav">
                          [: range $name, $resource := $api.Resources :]
                          <li><a href="/reference/[: $api.ID :]/resource/[: $name :]">[: $resource.Title :]</a></li>
                          [: end :]
                      </ul>
                  </li>
                  <li>Swagger
                      <ul class="nav">
                          <li><a class="sub_link" href="/spec/swagger.json">Download</a></li>
                      </ul>
                  </li>
-->
              </ul>
          </li>
        [: end :]
    </ul>
</div>
